        </item>
        <item>
            <title>香港摄影大赛得奖结果公布，南昌押霓虹招牌拆前「遗作」获选佳作</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2024/03/06/hong-kong-photo-contest/dc/photogism/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=hong-kong-photo-contest</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2024/03/06/hong-kong-photo-contest/dc/photogism/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[蒋纳偲]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Wed, 06 Mar 2024 15:00:29 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[摄影文化]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[香港摄影大赛]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1222816</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>《国家地理》杂志举办的 2023 年香港摄影大赛昨日揭晓，展现了来自各行各业摄影爱好者的精彩视角。此次大赛共吸引了 9,205 件作品参赛，涵盖城市、生态、风景、人物、历史建筑以及手机摄影六大类别。评审团由国际及本地的摄影大师组成，包括国家地理资深生态摄影师 Tim Laman、香港知名摄影艺术家郑振扬，以及《国家地理》中文版的总编辑李永适。</p><p>在各类别中尤其引人注目的是历史建筑组别，其中一幅以昔日深水埗南昌押的霓虹招牌为主题的作品，记录了这个标志性景象的最后光辉。这幅名为《南昌押》的照片由朱伟民拍摄，展示了南昌押那不再复见的霓虹招牌。值得一提的是，南昌押的霓虹招牌因不符合现行的《建筑物条例》而于去年 3 月被拆除，此后由保育团体「霓虹交汇」在元朗负责保存。</p><p><img decoding="async" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-1222819" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/screenshot20240306at-10-694x463.png" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/screenshot20240306at-10-694x463.png 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/screenshot20240306at-10.png 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>历史建筑组别的冠军作品则是由陈洁冰创作的《人生路》，这幅作品巧妙地捕捉了黄大仙祠的独特面貌，向我们展示了香港丰富的文化遗产和摄影师们如何通过镜头将这些瞬间永久地定格。</p><p><img decoding="async" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-1222832" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/screenshot20240306at-11-694x495.png" alt="" width="694" height="495" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/screenshot20240306at-11-694x495.png 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/screenshot20240306at-11.png 1261w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><h2>以下部分参赛作品：</h2><p>风景组：</p><p>冠军作品：《动力之源》金冠华</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-1222843" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/screenshot20240306at-12-694x460.png" alt="" width="694" height="460" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/screenshot20240306at-12-694x460.png 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/screenshot20240306at-12.png 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>亚军作品：《雾上航行》谢汉明</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-1222844" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/screenshot20240306at-13-694x464.png" alt="" width="694" height="464" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/screenshot20240306at-13-694x464.png 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/screenshot20240306at-13.png 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>季军作品：《大佛云雾缭绕》张贻彬</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-1222845" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/screenshot20240306at-14-694x463.png" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/screenshot20240306at-14-694x463.png 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/screenshot20240306at-14.png 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>城市组：</p><p>冠军作品：《天梯》黄建荣</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-1222846" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/screenshot20240306at-15-694x460.png" alt="" width="694" height="460" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/screenshot20240306at-15-694x460.png 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/screenshot20240306at-15.png 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>亚军作品：《乐园》翟广文</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-1222847" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/screenshot20240306at-16-694x459.png" alt="" width="694" height="459" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/screenshot20240306at-16-694x459.png 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/screenshot20240306at-16.png 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>季军作品：《旺角街头》田隽恺</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-1222848" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/screenshot20240306at-17-381x580.png" alt="" width="381" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/screenshot20240306at-17-381x580.png 381w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/screenshot20240306at-17.png 592w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 381px" /></p><p>历史建筑组：</p><p>冠军作品：《人生路》陈洁冰</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-1222849" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/screenshot20240306at-18-694x554.png" alt="" width="694" height="554" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/screenshot20240306at-18-694x554.png 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/screenshot20240306at-18.png 1127w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>亚军作品：《撑伞人》李健陶</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-1222850" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/screenshot20240306at-19-694x555.png" alt="" width="694" height="555" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/screenshot20240306at-19-694x555.png 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/screenshot20240306at-19.png 1126w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>季军作品：《我在明，你在暗！》陈辉</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-1222851" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/screenshot20240306at-20-442x580.png" alt="" width="442" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/screenshot20240306at-20-442x580.png 442w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/screenshot20240306at-20.png 685w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 442px" /></p><p>其余的得奖作品可以透过<a href="https://hkphotocontest.com/exhibition.asp">网上虚拟展览形式</a>免费参观，或由即日起至 3 月 24 日都可以于线下参加实体展览：九龙尖沙咀海港城广东道 23 号太子酒店 3 楼 SAVVY。</p><p>资料来源：<a href="https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E5%9C%96%E8%BC%AF%EF%BD%9C%E9%A6%99%E